(Trypanosoma Evansi is widely distributed monomorphic protozoan which infects pet and large animals such as dogs\054 camels\054 equines and) Tj
T*
(cattle\056 The organism also has been found infecting cats\056 Trypanosoma Evansi is mechanically transmitted by blood sucking insect species\056) Tj
T*
(The parasite destroys red blood cells\054 provoking serious and often fatal anaemia\056) Tj
T*
